snippet.textDisplay: I gotta say Floss, I watch pretty much all the reviews put out for every new device. And I must say, I always save you for last because your reviews always help me make my (REAL) final decision. Nothin against the other creators out there, they are doing their thing and good on them.... but with you, I feel like it is personal. I feel like you always give it straight and that you tell it as you see it. No flashy review "studio" (although no doubt you could have one if you wanted). No colorful background ambient lighting. Hell, you don't even post yourself in the vids cause at the end of the day you are reviewing a phone for us, not showing off your newest swag to sell or whatknot. Nope... we just get your hands, white shoes (love that got damn cat!) and the kit your reviewing. Which is all we need. Just the way I like it. So Keep on Keeping On brother cause you still got what no one else has. And that's straight up hustle. Givin the people what they want, when and how they want it. Congrats on not needing to be something/someone else! Keepin it REAL Floss. Cheers brother!
